{"title":"西藏萨迦格言","authors":["王尧选"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":11,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏萨迦格言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正直的人虽然碰到生命的危难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不会捐弃自己的本性；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天然黄金虽然经过烧熔冶炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么也不会改变它本来的颜色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胆小的人不管聚集了多少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不能完成伟大的事业；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泽江草不管捆了许多，〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不能充当大厦的栋梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：泽江草：草名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王尧选译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}